    • from

      static ConnectExecutionStrategy from(ExecutionStrategy executionStrategy)
      Converts the provided execution strategy to a ConnectExecutionStrategy. If the provided strategy is already ConnectExecutionStrategy it is returned unchanged. For other strategies, if the strategy ExecutionStrategy.hasOffloads() then offloadAll() is returned otherwise offloadNone() is returned.
